# Claude Code Plugins

This project uses the Equal AI Toolkit from `claude-skills`.

## Installation

```bash
# Add the marketplace (one-time)
/plugin marketplace add your-org/claude-skills

# Install the toolkit
/plugin install equal-ai-toolkit@claude-skills
```

## First-Run Setup

Run `/investigate-alert` to complete the one-time configuration. This sets up both:
- **SRE Investigation** - Alert debugging and RCA reports
- **Integration Test Expert** - Test generation using production data

Configuration is saved to `.claude/config/toolkit-config.yaml`.

## Usage

### SRE Investigation

```bash
# Investigate latest alert
/investigate-alert

# Investigate specific issue
/investigate-alert "5xx errors on api-service"
```

### Integration Tests

Mention "integration tests", "e2e test", or "test my API" to trigger the expert.

